#: ../../M/marketroid.rst:5
msgid "marketroid"
msgstr "marketroid"

#: ../../M/marketroid.rst:7
msgid "/mar´k\\@·troyd/, n\\."
msgstr "/mar´k\\@·troyd/, 名詞"

#: ../../M/marketroid.rst:9
msgid ""
"alt. : marketing slime, marketeer, mar­ket­ing droid, marketdroid. A member "
"of a company's marketing department, esp. one who promises users that the "
"next version of a product will have features that are not actually scheduled"
" for inclusion, are extremely difficult to implement, and/or are in "
"violation of the laws of physics; and/or one who describes existing features"
" (and misfeatures) in ebullient, buzzword-laden adspeak. Derogatory. Compare"
" :ref:`droid`\\."
msgstr ""
"別案:marketing slime、marketeer、marketing "
"droid、marketdroid。会社のマーケティング部門のメンバー、特に、製品の次のバージョンに実際には組み込み予定のない、実装が極めて困難な、かつ/または物理法則に反する機能が付くとユーザーに約束する者。かつ/または、既存の機能(と欠陥機能)を、熱狂的でバズワードまみれの広告口調で描写する者。侮蔑的。\\"
" :ref:`droid`\\ と比較せよ。"
